item.title: Need Help
item.dc:creator: @doom_j doom_j
item.description:
@doom_j wrote:

skillpksftw:

Wow thanks for being nice jesus, i didnt know im new on mopar and i did make a effort thanks i would just like a better coder than myself before buying vps and stuff.

You can’t just ask for a coder, but you can in fact create a development topic in the team development section to get other members of the community to help with things like programing the server and client, helping you to create a site, etc, but you will need to post updates on what you have accomplished. I should also point out people here won’t code for you for the fun of it or respect. Most people here will only do it for profit like money…

[quote=“zyle1992, post:6, topic:392622”][quote author=skillpksftw link=topic=489795.msg3580905#msg3580905 date=1303782449]
Wow thanks for being nice jesus, i didnt know im new on mopar and i did make a effort thanks i would just like a better coder than myself before buying vps and stuff.
[/quote]

Then learn how to program before you buy a vps/dedicated server[/quote]

Also this, you need to learn how to program your self… A good start is looking at the sticky threads in a lot of the sections, they’re filled with tons of information that can help you learn how to program in Java or another language and also show you how the RS2 protocol works.
